{"type":"answer","id":9762,"parentType":"question","parentId":2199,"uid":1655,"contents":"京品游戏。<br>\n<br>\n该游戏充满了中国特色社会主义，有利于党中央人物从群众中来，到群众里去的根本需要，加强人民对我党人物(比如<b>习特勒、江索里尼和吴列宁</b>)的认识。<br>\n<br>\n建议加上角色：<b>庆大帝、江贤者、维尼包，萨格尔王，曹丰泽</b>(这个就算了)。<br>\n<br>\n图为角色设想<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20180808/1533702494952319.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20180808/1533702494952319.jpg\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20180808/1533702494952319.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20180808/1533702519922376.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20180808/1533702519922376.jpg\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20180808/1533702519922376.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2018-08-08","agreeCount":6,"discussionCount":0}